WEBVTT

12:56.830 --> 12:57.710 line:80%
Although it can't compare to

12:57.710 --> 12:59.640 line:80%
the exquisite food at Yixiang Restaurant,

12:59.640 --> 13:00.920 line:80%
it's better because we're together.

13:00.920 --> 13:01.830 line:80%
Yes, indeed.

13:01.920 --> 13:02.950 line:80%
Thank you, Auntie.

13:02.950 --> 13:04.670 line:80%
It's been a long time since
I had mutton dumplings.

13:04.670 --> 13:05.550 line:80%
Let me help too.

13:05.670 --> 13:06.310 line:80%
No need.
